//This is my first script for the wiimote. It hasn't got support for
//the numchuck and camera functions (it becomes crazy when you move
//the wiimote). For the four functions (light, health, binoculars and
//change weapons) press home + up down left or right. If you can fix
//the camera problem, please fix it.

// The following is for turning wii button presses into keyboard presses and mouse clicks 
w = Wiimote.Up 
s = Wiimote.Down 
a = Wiimote.Left 
d = Wiimote.Right 
space = Wiimote.B = false 
q = Wiimote.One 
f = Wiimote.Two 
h = Wiimote.A and wiimote.B 
g = Wiimote.A 
z = Wiimote.Minus 
tab = wiimote.Plus and wiimote.Minus 
e = wiimote.Home 
home = wiimote.home and wiimote.Up 
end = wiimote.home and wiimote.Down 
del = wiimote.home and wiimote.Left 
pagedown = wiimote.home and wiimote.Right 



